# Google Cloud *Desktop* OAuth client secret — next non-comment line. Required by Google on token exchange + refresh alongside PKCE.
# Copy this file to google-oauth-client-secret.txt and replace the last line with your real GOCSPX-... secret from Google Cloud Console.
